.TH SESSIOND 8 "@HIDLOOM_VERSION@" "HIDloom" "System Administration"
.SH NAME
sessiond \- local PTY/session helper daemon
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B python3 -m sessiond.sessiond
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B sessiond
provides local session and PTY helper functions used by logicd companion
features. It is normally started on demand.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B -h, --help
Show command help.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR logicd (8)
.br
